			<description><![CDATA[<p>
PayPerks is looking for a senior level Test Engineer to lead and grow our QA department. You will work closely with the engineering team to develop an agile process for automated system tests, maintain the existing test suite and create the new tests themselves.</p>
<p>
Responsibilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Build out and maintain the automated test suite, using a combination of Python, Webdriver and Selenium.</li>
<li>
Identify workflows that are candidates for automated system tests, and coordinate manual tests for those that are not.</li>
<li>
Manage small team of manual QA testers</li>
<li>
Participate in iteration planning, providing input on automated testing tasks and associated effort for the selected user stories.</li>
<li>
Create and manage bug reports, ensuring they are clearly communicated to the team and addressed in a timely, thorough, and satisfactory manner.</li>
<li>
Provide feedback and recommendations on software usability and functionality.</li>
<li>
Partner with DevOps to deliver continuously running health-checks on the entire production system.</li>
</ul>
<p>
Requirements:</p>
<ul>
<li>
3+ years experience in a test automation role, with emphasis on software and/or browser-based service testing.</li>
<li>
Solid experience with Python and Webriver / Selenium; or experience with similar tools and ability to learn quickly.</li>
<li>
Expertise in automated test suite development and maintenance.</li>
<li>
Ease and comfort with how quality assurance and the QA role fits within the Agile software development process.</li>
<li>
Ability to develop standards, methods, or procedures to determine release quality and production readiness.</li>
<li>
Must be a US Citizen or US Permanent Resident</li>
</ul>
<p>
PayPerks is a VC-backed, fintech startup based in Flatiron, NYC that is building a pioneering education and loyalty platform revolutionizing financial services for millions of low and middle income consumers.&nbsp; We&#39;ve been recognized by the White House, called the &quot;Next Big Thing in Prepaid&quot; and have a for profit, social impact mission.&nbsp; This will make your mom proud.</p>
<p>
If this sounds like something you&#39;re interested in, get in touch.</p>
<p>
--</p>
<p>
